function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

}

	} else if (sha1_file('dev/test_path_functions.php') != '4aa213aa12c3d340f7017b230ab22237ae83bba9') {

				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_1();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/test_path_functions.php') !== '4aa213aa12c3d340f7017b230ab22237ae83bba9') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/test_path_functions.php');

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') != 'a0b5da4c9cd4a244a16aba0558c76dc4381059ae') {

	}

	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') !== 'a0b5da4c9cd4a244a16aba0558c76dc4381059ae') {

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/domain/OIDplusDomain.class.php');
	writefile_28();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/domain/OIDplusDomain.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/domain/OIDplusDomain.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/domain/OIDplusDomain.class.php') != '2fc183fc112f94a69b3bb4ee79d6714330b480e6') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/domain/OIDplusDomain.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/domain/OIDplusDomain.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/domain/OIDplusDomain.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/domain/OIDplusDomain.class.php') !== '2fc183fc112f94a69b3bb4ee79d6714330b480e6') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/domain/OIDplusDomain.class.php') !== '19ce653b3579e696122abb76e8e31d378870dc2a') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/domain/OIDplusDomain.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/domain/OIDplusDomain.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/domain/OIDplusDomain.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/domain/OIDplusDomain.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_28();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/domain/OIDplusDomain.class.php') !== '2fc183fc112f94a69b3bb4ee79d6714330b480e6') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/domain/OIDplusDomain.class.php');
		}

	writefile_30();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/guid/OIDplusGuid.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/guid/OIDplusGuid.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/guid/OIDplusGuid.class.php') != 'ce59646eff89a5da53c76bf843a74f42ea2b7302') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/guid/OIDplusGuid.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/guid/OIDplusGuid.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/guid/OIDplusGuid.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/guid/OIDplusGuid.class.php') !== 'ce59646eff89a5da53c76bf843a74f42ea2b7302') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/guid/OIDplusGuid.class.php') !== '53368ac42bb0f922f37f64f8b5addbbdb3332df1') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/guid/OIDplusGuid.class.php');

			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/guid/OIDplusGuid.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_30();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/guid/OIDplusGuid.class.php') !== 'ce59646eff89a5da53c76bf843a74f42ea2b7302') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/guid/OIDplusGuid.class.php');

			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/092_forgot_password_admin/OIDplusPagePublicForgotPasswordAdmin.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/092_forgot_password_admin/OIDplusPagePublicForgotPasswordAdmin.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_39();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/092_forgot_password_admin/OIDplusPagePublicForgotPasswordAdmin.class.php') !== '14d1cc069a49f238d5ba05baa06bc3437b746f58') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/092_forgot_password_admin/OIDplusPagePublicForgotPasswordAdmin.class.php');
		}
	}
}

			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_43();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') !== '1567bd312aeab502fe7c575769b1d34236017cdc') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
		}
	}
}

			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/OIDplusPagePublicFreeOID.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/OIDplusPagePublicFreeOID.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_44();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/OIDplusPagePublicFreeOID.class.php') !== 'bb6cf19480da133e32c5bad54bfba36f2b639172') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/OIDplusPagePublicFreeOID.class.php');
		}
	}
}
